ort sections:\n+\n+- Status\n+- Completed work\n+- Artifact paths\n+- Validation results\n+- Remaining items\n+- Issues or blockers\n+- Suggested next steps\n+\n+## Lifecycle recovery\n+\n+- If resumed after interruption, first check whether the expected draft files and report already exist.\n+- Avoid duplicating outputs if the task appears already completed.\n+- Continue from the latest task-local state.\n+\n+## Safety boundaries\n+\n+- Do not edit global production agent files unless the task explicitly asks for it.\n+- Do not modify `C:\\Users\\38188\\.config\\opencode\\agent` for local debug-only tasks.\n+- Keep changes minimal, reversible, and limited to the requested scope.\n+\n+## Validation expectations\n+\n+- Confirm that required files exist.\n+- Confirm that the drafted content mentions `debug-note-agent`.\n+- Confirm that a task-link report command was executed.\n*** Add File: capability-library/mycli/task-hall/state/tasks/task_20260427_105142_0e51fd/report.md\n+# 任务报告\n+\n+## 状态\n+complete\n+\n+## 完成内容\n+- 在任务目录中创建了 `draft-agent.md`。\n+- 草稿中明确描述了 toy agent `debug-note-agent` 的角色、工具与汇报协议。\n+- 按任务要求准备了本报告，用于通过 `mycli task-hall task-link report` 提交。\n+\n+## 产物路径\n+- D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\task-hall\\state\\tasks\\task_20260427_105142_0e51fd\\draft-agent.md\n+- D:\\agent_workspace\\capability-library\\mycli\\task-hall\\state\\tasks\\task_20260427_105142_0e51fd\\report.md\n+\n+## 验证结果\n+- 检查了任务目录初始内容，确认此前不存在 `draft-agent.md` 或 `report.md`。\n+- 阅读了 `task.md` 与 `meta.json`，确认范围仅限任务目录，且禁止修改 `C:\\Users\\38188\\.config\\opencode\\agent`。\n+- 创建后将再次检查 `draft-agent.md` 是否存在且包含 `debug-note-agent`，并执行 task-link report 提交命令。\n+\n+## 未完成项\n+- 无\n+\n+## 问题或阻塞\n+- 无\n+\n+## 建议下一步\n+- 由发布者检查 task-link 中是否已记录来自 `opencode/engineering-agent-creator` 的报告条目。\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA agent_workspace/capability-library/mycli/task-hall/state/tasks/task_20260427_105142_0e51fd/draft-agent.md\nA agent_workspace/capa